{"id":"errors/NG2009","title":"NG2009: Component selector does not match shadow DOM requirements\n\n元件選擇器與 Shadow DOM 的要求不匹配","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/errors/NG2009.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements元件選擇器與-shadow-dom-的要求不匹配\">NG2009: Component selector does not match shadow DOM requirements\n\n元件選擇器與 Shadow DOM 的要求不匹配<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements元件選擇器與-shadow-dom-的要求不匹配\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a></code> 的元件的選擇器與自訂元素標記名稱的要求不匹配。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The selector of a component using <code><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a></code> doesn't match the custom element tag name requirements.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為了使標籤名稱被視為有效的自訂元素名稱，它必須：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In order for a tag name to be considered a valid custom element name, it has to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">是小寫的。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Be in lower case.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">包含連字元。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Contain a hyphen.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以字母（a-z）開頭。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Start with a letter (a-z).</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"如何排除本錯誤\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#如何排除本錯誤\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"debugging-the-error\">Debugging the error<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">重新命名元件的選擇器，使其符合要求。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Rename your component's selector so that it matches the requirements.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>之前：</strong></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>Before:</strong></p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'comp',\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>\n  …\n})\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>之後：</strong></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>After:</strong></p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app-comp',\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>\n  …\n})\n\n</code-example>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\n - errors/NG2009#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG2009#description\n - errors/NG2009#ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements元件選擇器與-shadow-dom-的要求不匹配\n - errors/NG2009#如何排除本錯誤\n - errors/NG2009#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/errors/NG2009.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}